African Union Mission in Burundi (AMIB) bụ ọrụ udo nke mpaghara nke African Union zigara na Burundi na 2003 n'oge ikpeazụ nke Agha Obodo Burundi.  Ozi a, nke nwere ndị agha 2,870 sitere na South Africa, Mozambique na Etiopia, nọrọ na mba ahụ otu afọ, mgbe United Nations Operation na Burundi (ONUB) nọchiri anya ya n'okpuru United Nations.Mbufe nke ikike site na AMIB gaa na ONUB mere na 1 June 2004
Akụkụ South Africa nke ndị agha ahụ nọgidere ma guzobe ya n'ime African Union Special Task Force (AU STF).
